                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New Orleans</placeName>\n                <date>March 16 1857</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>Dear <addressee>Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I hasten to inform<lb/> you that yesterday the members<lb/> of the\n                Home assembled at that<lb/> Institution to elect such officers<lb/> whose term had\n                expired viz a President<lb/> 1<hi rend=\"sup\">st</hi> Vice &amp; 2<hi rend=\"sup\"\n                    >nd</hi> Vice President Treasurer<lb/> Sec'y &amp; one half of the Trustees</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The Board now stands thus</p>\n            <list type=\"simple\">\n                <head/>\n                <item><persName>M M Simpson</persName> President re elected</item>\n                <item><persName>Geo Jonas</persName> 1<hi rend=\"sup\">st</hi> vice Do new</item>\n                <item><persName>Abm Staher</persName> 2<hi rend=\"sup\">nd</hi> vice Do new</item>\n                <item><persName>Danl Goodman</persName> Treasurer reelected</item>\n                <item><persName>Revd J K Gutheim</persName> Secy Do</item>\n            </list>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Directors</p>\n            <p>same as before except <persName>Mr<lb/> DC Labatt</persName> is elected<lb/> to fill\n                the place of <persName>L L Levy Esq</persName><lb/> who like myself &amp; the Hon\n                    <persName>H<lb/> M Hyams</persName> declined a re election<lb/> on time not\n                permitting</p>\n            <p>The Hebrew Ball was as grand affair<lb/> crowded &amp; the Elite &amp; high officials\n                of our<lb/> city in attendance the profit is over<lb/> $2300 yours in haste</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Isaac Hart</persName>\n            </p>\n            "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3z89318d/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
